<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Jhors Electric - Mobile Accessories</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header {
      background: #222;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 0;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .container {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .product {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      width: 280px;
      margin: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .product:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    h2 {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
    }
    .price {
      color: #e91e63;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    footer {
      background: #222;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 0;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>⚡ Jhors Electric - Mobile Accessories ⚡</header>

<div class="container">
  <div class="product">
    <img src="charger.jpg" alt="Mobile Charger">
    <h2>Fast Mobile Charger</h2>
    <p>High-speed charging with durable design.</p>
    <p class="price">₹299</p>
  </div>

  <div class="product">
    <img src="usb-cable.jpg" alt="USB Cable">
    <h2>USB Cable</h2>
    <p>Strong, flexible and fast data transfer cable.</p>
    <p class="price">₹149</p>
  </div>

  <div class="product">
    <img src="adapter.jpg" alt="Power Adapter">
    <h2>Power Adapter</h2>
    <p>Compact and reliable power adapter for all devices.</p>
    <p class="price">₹249</p>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2025 Jhors Electric | All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</body>
</html>
